	(text_box "Voltage divider to set TADJ pin for optimum performance depending on frequency.\n\nFor first prototype, a trimmer is included to allow precise tuning from a 3.32V VPOS rail.\nTrimmer at minimum: 0.8017V\nTrimmer at maximum: 0.8713V\n\nThis allows tuning between 900MHz & 1.9GHz from table 4 in datasheet (see inset).\n\nReplace with simple voltage divider when optimum TADJ voltage is known."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 196.85 81.28 0)
		(size 35.56 81.28)
		(margins 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525)
